===Specifications=== :[http://item.gmarket.co.kr/Item?goodscode=1199388192 ''Humax Quantum T9x'' on '''GMarket'''] *CPU: [[Intel (Lantiq)]] PXB4395 @1.6GHz (GRX350 Dual Core) *Flash: 256MB (NAND), RAM: 512MB (DDR3), USB: USB 3.0 *WLAN: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] [[Lantiq#WAVE500|WAVE500]] Series (Wave2, MU-MIMO) :2.4GHz: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] PSB 83513M (3T3R 802.11bgn) :5GHz: [[Lantiq (Intel)]] PSB 83524M (4T4R 802.11an/ac) *Ports: 1x WAN GbE, 4x LAN GbE; 1x USB 3.0, 1x USB 2.0; *Power Adapter: DC 12V/2.5A *Dimensions: 261x164x36 mm (WxDxH) *Weight: 718g
